'''天主教巴門達總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Bamendana}}；{{lang-fr|Archidiocèse de Bamenda}}）是[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄三個教區。此總教區是該國五個總教區之一。

總教區的前身、巴門達教區於1970年8月13日成立，1982年3月18日升為總教區。<ref>{{cite web |title=YAUNDENSIS ET ALIARUM* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19820312_yaundensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-12-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231122327/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19820312_yaundensis.html |archivedate=2019-12-31 |language=la |date=1982-03-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

總教區位於[[西北省_(喀麥隆)|西北省]]部，2006年時有教友252,000人（佔轄區總人口21.6%）、廿八個堂區和九十二名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-fr|安德肋·恩基阿·富安亞|Andrew Nkea Fuanya}}<ref name="Vatican20191230">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 30.12.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/30/191230a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-12-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231110154/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/30/191230a.html |archivedate=2019-12-31 |language=en |date=2019-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|彌額爾·米阿貝蘇·比比|Michael Miabesue Bibi}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Other Pontifical Acts, 24.01.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/01/24/170124f.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-12-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231120128/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/01/24/170124f.html |archivedate=2019-12-31 |language=en |date=2017-01-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|科爾乃略·豐滕·埃蘇阿|Cornelius Fontem Esua}}<ref name="Vatican20191230" />。

